  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/68ec8c687d123e44395f7b5b428a6f58.poster.avif?t=1706274513\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/68ec8c687d123e44395f7b5b428a6f58.webm?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/68ec8c687d123e44395f7b5b428a6f58.mp4?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to a world of distorted minds</strong><br><br>Mycorrhiza is a love letter to horror manga in the form of a visual novel. Some of our biggest inspirations include the works of Junji Ito and Masaaki Nakayama.<br><br>While Scott is trying to find a way back home, reality distorts and people’s morals start shifting in cruel and unexpected ways. A peculiar plant transforming animals, a horrifying comedy trend and a strange building trapping people. Each of the three arcs explores different terrors.<br><br>As you explore this terrifying world, you'll find out more and more about how and why Scott is trapped in it and what lead up to Scott being spirited away.<br><br><strong>Join us on our adventure into despair.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/534fb33eaab3898a17956d4dea2e9ff6.poster.avif?t=1706274513\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/534fb33eaab3898a17956d4dea2e9ff6.webm?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/534fb33eaab3898a17956d4dea2e9ff6.mp4?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Three individual, yet interconnected horrifying stories.<br></li><li> Writing and art inspired by horror manga's greatest.<br></li><li> Animated CGs.<br></li><li> Art drawn by a horror manga artist.<br></li><li> Elaborate audio implementation.<br></li><li> Accessibility options such as visual audio cues and dyslexic font.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/9d4fd05bb1cf91624cb0831dbd1366e5.poster.avif?t=1706274513\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/9d4fd05bb1cf91624cb0831dbd1366e5.webm?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/9d4fd05bb1cf91624cb0831dbd1366e5.mp4?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/68ec8c687d123e44395f7b5b428a6f58.poster.avif?t=1706274513\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/68ec8c687d123e44395f7b5b428a6f58.webm?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/68ec8c687d123e44395f7b5b428a6f58.mp4?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to a world of distorted minds</strong><br><br>Mycorrhiza is a love letter to horror manga in the form of a visual novel. Some of our biggest inspirations include the works of Junji Ito and Masaaki Nakayama.<br><br>While Scott is trying to find a way back home, reality distorts and people’s morals start shifting in cruel and unexpected ways. A peculiar plant transforming animals, a horrifying comedy trend and a strange building trapping people. Each of the three arcs explores different terrors.<br><br>As you explore this terrifying world, you'll find out more and more about how and why Scott is trapped in it and what lead up to Scott being spirited away.<br><br><strong>Join us on our adventure into despair.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/534fb33eaab3898a17956d4dea2e9ff6.poster.avif?t=1706274513\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/534fb33eaab3898a17956d4dea2e9ff6.webm?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/534fb33eaab3898a17956d4dea2e9ff6.mp4?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Three individual, yet interconnected horrifying stories.<br></li><li> Writing and art inspired by horror manga's greatest.<br></li><li> Animated CGs.<br></li><li> Art drawn by a horror manga artist.<br></li><li> Elaborate audio implementation.<br></li><li> Accessibility options such as visual audio cues and dyslexic font.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/9d4fd05bb1cf91624cb0831dbd1366e5.poster.avif?t=1706274513\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/9d4fd05bb1cf91624cb0831dbd1366e5.webm?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128560/extras/9d4fd05bb1cf91624cb0831dbd1366e5.mp4?t=1706274513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
